items.title: Monthly Meetup - February Talks
items.summary:
We're really excited to have a fantastic community speaker coming along from far-afield: Kevin Jump (Mr uSync)

Agenda:
1800 - If you're super early, feel free to come and say hi.
1830 - Open for social and mingling
